These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, prince, old-henry
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, june
City: marseilles, edinburgh, colone
1. the prince-smoker is between the indian and the person traveling to marseilles##2
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the thai##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the indian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Cigar          | ritmeester      | prince        | old-henry     |
| Nationality         | malaysian | thai | indian    |
| Birthday   | december   | august       | june |
| City         | marseilles  | edinburgh      | colone    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, rose, azalea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, baccarat, aristoff
City: nizza, london, paris
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, iced-tea
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is the person who growsrose##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
6. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking iced-tea is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Flower           | rose    | azalea | sunflower |
| Cigar   | baccarat | bongani       | aristoff   |
| City           | paris  | london   | nizza     |
| Beverage         | lemonade | iced-tea       | fanta   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, turkish, german
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, ritmeester, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, october
City: edinburgh, liverpool, venice
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the german is the person traveling to venice##1
3. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
4. the french is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person traveling to venice##2
5. the old-henry-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Nationality          | german | french | turkish |
| Cigar   | montecristo     | old-henry | ritmeester |
| Birthday           | july       | june   | october    |
| City     | venice      | edinburgh   | liverpool |

