.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, monopoly
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, van, roller
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, milk
There 3 different types of food: pepper, mango, lemon
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person driving the roller is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
6. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
7. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Game         | backgammon  | scrabble       | monopoly |
| Transport           | roller     | van      | helicopter   |
| Beverage   | sprite | soy-milk | milk     |
| Food   | pepper      | lemon   | mango     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, daisy
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, january
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, woodworking, hiking
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, palace
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
7. the palace house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Flower      | daisy     | sunflower   | dahlia         |
| Birthday           | march | september | january |
| Hobby   | hiking      | woodworking   | traveling            |
| House   | gothic-revival   | palace  | farmhouse         |

