.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, pop, rock
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, august
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, juice
House: tower, wooden, farmhouse
1. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's birthday is in september and the fan of pop##2
2. the tower house is the fan of house##1
3. the person drinking juice is the wooden house##1
4. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the tower house is in an even position##4
6. the tower house is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Music-Genre          | rock    | house     | pop |
| Birthday           | september | august | march      |
| Beverage   | juice      | 7up       | mirinda    |
| House   | wooden      | tower         | farmhouse     |

