.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, mexican, nigerian
House: craftsman, townhouse, cape-cod
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, chef, police-officer
1. the polish is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the polish##1
3. the cape-cod house is the chef##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
5. the nigerian is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the chef and the mexican##2
7. the police-officer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Nationality          | mexican | polish | nigerian |
| House   | townhouse  | craftsman    | cape-cod |
| Hobby   | fishing  | drawing   | sudoku    |
| Job     | police-officer   | electrician       | chef |

