.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
City: hannover, venice, san-francisco
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, sunflower
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, alhambra, fonseca
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, house, indie
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of house is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the fan of house is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
7. the person who growsdaffodil is between the alhambra-smoker and the fan of indie##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| City      | venice | hannover    | san-francisco  |
| Flower         | sunflower        | daffodil   | orchid   |
| Cigar   | fonseca       | havana    | alhambra |
| Music-Genre     | indie          | house | classical       |

