.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, emerald, ebony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, lacrosse
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, goat
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, sunflower
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Color           | aquamarine     | ebony    | emerald |
| Sport   | skiing  | volleyball | lacrosse      |
| Pet   | goat       | fish   | rabbit    |
| Flower     | amaryllis | sunflower        | daffodil     |

