4. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person traveling to boston is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
