3. the victorian house is on the far right##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the person driving the train##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
7. the russian is between the turkish and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
