3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, swisher, bolivar
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4
4. the wooden house is on the far right##1
5. the person watching drama movies is the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the modern house is in the middle##1
7. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
9. the modern house is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| City           | nizza | hannover   | liverpool |
| House   | palace  | modern    | wooden    |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy    | drama | comedy   |
| Cigar     | swisher  | bolivar     | aristoff  |

