2. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to prague and the person driving the quad-bike##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the wooden house##1
4. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2        |     3      |
