.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, satire, mystery
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, fanta
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, ferret
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, may
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre          | satire  | western   | mystery |
| Beverage   | lemonade      | fanta      | hot-chocolate   |
| Pet   | hedgehog     | ferret | goat |
| Birthday         | october | september   | may   |

