.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, cooking
There 3 different types of food: apricot, avocado, peach
3 different games are played: billiard, canasta, bridge
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Hobby           | writing  | cooking | rock-climbing   |
| Food   | avocado | peach           | apricot      |
| Game           | bridge   | canasta          | billiard |
| Beverage     | lemonade    | mirinda           | tea |

 